═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="csd-strategies">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="csd-strategies__head">
      <h2>Proven Strategies for Success</h2>
      <p>Effective strategies are the foundation of project success. By establishing clear goals, defining actionable steps, and anticipating potential challenges, we ensure each phase of development aligns with your vision and objectives.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="csd-strategy">
      <div class="csd-strategy__card">
        <div class="csd-strategy__icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i></div>
        <h3>Design Process</h3>
        <p>Through our proven design process, we have created hundreds of unique interfaces for web and mobile platforms.</p>
      </div>
      <ol class="csd-strategy__list">
        <li><span class="csd-strategy__num">1</span><div><h4>Map User Flow Diagrams</h4><p>We start by understanding your users and goals, creating detailed user flow diagrams to define how people will interact with your product.</p></div></li>
        <li><span class="csd-strategy__num">2</span><div><h4>Create Low-Fidelity Wireframes</h4><p>Next, we translate flows into clean, low-fidelity wireframes that focus on layout, structure, and core functionality — without distractions.</p></div></li>
        <li><span class="csd-strategy__num">3</span><div><h4>Iterate with Your Feedback</h4><p>We review and refine designs collaboratively, incorporating your feedback to ensure everything aligns with your vision and user needs.</p></div></li>
        <li><span class="csd-strategy__num">4</span><div><h4>Deliver a Dev-Ready Prototype</h4><p>Finally, we hand off a high-fidelity, interactive prototype that's fully annotated and ready for a smooth transition into development.</p></div></li>
      </ol>
